This Saturday April 17, 7pm Bin100 corner of US1 and Landsdale Ave. Milford. I heard they are excellent!

Contemporary Jazz / Smooth Jazz & Vocals / World Fusion


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Airborne the "Musical Peacemakers" of Contemporary Jazz
sends a Inspirational Message of Hope to the World

A beautiful trademark jazz sound of island passion and urban emotion

Their next and 7th CD "New Horizons" will be released in May of 2010

In ancient times the word Horizons meant across the World.

Airborne's hope for a new world is ever present in this next CD.

Remember we are One World - One People searching for Peace and "New Horizons"
